      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1610762365,
      "updated": 1610762365
    },
    {
      "id": "6002487d5b98c200006d6793",
      "text": "書類を内容別に分類して格納するのではなく、[時系列]に並べてしまう方式。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1610762365,
      "updated": 1610847944
    },
    {
      "id": "6002487e5b98c200006d6794",
      "text": "英語では、なぜか「[Noguchi Filing System]」というらしい",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1610762367,
      "updated": 1610763970
    },
    {
      "id": "600248885b98c200006d6795",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1610762377,
      "updated": 1610762377
    },
    {
      "id": "600248db5b98c200006d679c",
      "text": "[「超」整理法]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1610762460,
      "updated": 1610762469
    },
    {
      "id": "600248db5b98c200006d679d",
      "text": "[野口悠紀雄]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1610762460,
      "updated": 1668842445
    },
    {
      "id": "637883cd5b98c20000d8fd2d",
